s, timestamps |\n58\t| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers |\n59\t| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background, sheets, FAB surfaces |\n60\t\n61\t### Typography (Nunito)\n62\t\n63\t| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n64\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n65\t| `displayLarge` | 57pt | Bold (700) | 64pt | Week number hero |\n66\t| `headlineMedium` | 28pt | SemiBold (600) | 36pt | Screen title |\n67\t| `titleLarge` | 22pt | SemiBold (600) | 28pt | Section headers |\n68\t| `titleMedium` | 16pt | Medium (500) | 24pt | Subtitles, list item titles |\n69\t| `bodyLarge` | 16pt | Regular (400) | 24pt | Primary body text, descriptions |\n70\t| `bodyMedium` | 14pt | Regular (400) | 20pt | Secondary text, bullet items |\n71\t| `labelLarge` | 14pt | SemiBold (600) | 20pt | Button labels, chips |\n72\t| `caption` | 11pt | Medium (500) | 16pt | Badges, timestamps |\n73\t\n74\t### Spacing (8pt base)\n75\t\n76\t| Token | Value |\n77\t|---|---|\n78\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n79\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n80\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n81\t| `md` | 16dp |\n82\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n83\t| `xl` | 32dp |\n84\t| `xxl` | 48dp |\n85\t\n86\t### Corner Radius\n87\t\n88\t| Token | Value |\n89\t|---|---|\n90\t| `sm` | 8dp |\n91\t| `md` | 12dp |\n92\t| `lg` | 16dp |\n93\t| `full` | 999dp (pills) |\n94\t\n95\t### Motion\n96\t\n97\t| Token | Value |\n98\t|---|---|\n99\t| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n100\t| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n101\t| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n102\t\n103\t---\n104\t\n105\t## 6. Layout Rules\n106\t\n107\t### Scaffold Structure\n108\t\n109\t```\n110\tScaffold\n111\t├── AppBar (title: \"My Pregnancy\", no elevation, Lavender Tint background)\n112\t│   └── Back button (leading) → returns to Home\n113\t├── Body: PageView (week-by-week swiper)\n114\t│   └── Each page: SingleChildScrollView\n115\t│       ├── WeekHeroCard (full-width, ~40% screen height)\n116\t│       ├── BodyChangesCard\n117\t│       ├── BabyDevelopmentCard\n118\t│       └── SelfCareTipsCard\n119\t└── Bottom: DueDateSum