ing and sitting with good alignment to reduce back pain.',\n506\t        },\n507\t        {\n508\t          'title': 'Continue staying active',\n509\t          'detail':\n510\t              'Regular low-impact exercise like swimming or walking can help with circulation and energy.',\n511\t        },\n512\t        {\n513\t          'title': 'Start planning the nursery',\n514\t          'detail':\n515\t              'This is a great time to start thinking about nursery themes and gathering essential items.',\n516\t        },\n517\t      ],\n518\t    };\n519\t    return tips[week] ??\n520\t        [\n521\t          {\n522\t            'title': 'Stay hydrated',\n523\t            'detail': 'Drink plenty of water throughout the day.',\n524\t          },\n525\t          {\n526\t            'title': 'Rest when needed',\n527\t            'detail': 'Listen to your body and rest when you feel tired.',\n528\t          },\n529\t          {\n530\t            'title': 'Attend prenatal appointments',\n531\t            'detail': 'Regular check-ups help monitor your pregnancy progress.',\n532\t          },\n533\t        ];\n534\t  }\n535\t}\n536\t\n537\tclass _ExpandableTipTile extends StatelessWidget {\n538\t  final int number;\n539\t  final String title;\n540\t  final String detail;\n541\t  final bool isExpanded;\n542\t  final VoidCallback onTap;\n543\t\n544\t  const _ExpandableTipTile({\n545\t    required this.number,\n546\t    required this.title,\n547\t    required this.detail,\n548\t    required this.isExpanded,\n549\t    required this.onTap,\n550\t  });\n551\t\n552\t  @override\n553\t  Widget build(BuildContext context) {\n554\t    final theme = Theme.of(context);\n555\t    final colorScheme = theme.colorScheme;\n556\t    final textTheme = theme.textTheme;\n557\t\n558\t    return GestureDetector(\n559\t      onTap: onTap,\n560\t      child: Container(\n561\t        padding: const EdgeInsets.all(AppTheme.spaceSm),\n562\t        decoration: BoxDecoration(\n563\t          border: